02)--Projection: CAST(x.a AS Float64) AS a1
03)----Aggregate: groupBy=[[x.a]], aggr=[[]]
04)------SubqueryAlias: x
05)--------Projection: Int64(1) AS a
06)----------EmptyRelation
07)--Projection: x.a AS a1
08)----Aggregate: groupBy=[[x.a]], aggr=[[]]
09)------SubqueryAlias: x
10)--------Projection: Float64(1.1) AS a
11)----------EmptyRelation

